>\n輸到仆街,要人幫手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721竟然真係有人帶班人入去搞事，truth-hk721真相還原<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aDauweU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aDauweU</a>"},{"pid":"de979f4d7793edf461cf5be1e20798b314164004","tid":2210671,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5a4f0c940901316d57ee4a2d66fa70eae47ab71","tid":2210671,"uid":25858,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"TR3B 反重力飛機用來上太空用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"係反引力呀，用星球間既引力黎飛行，如果四周圍都無行星就飛唔到"},{"pid":"6d19449815f0d833f492ccdf270ac11a43edf198","tid":2210671,"uid":157411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:24:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩先成立完太空軍無幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8fcfaf5342d0b2a9e34d0ca8a3be77c1266203","tid":2210671,"uid":282053,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"quote":{"pid":"e6c97635c2bc32b111c40d7d1401f88c5b71d3ad","tid":2210671,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":187,"score":-187,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"好似柒左d....."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T17:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OP5SJeo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOP5SJeo.png&h=cdf5d314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至少冇你咁柒"},{"pid":"df273d66c4c0f9b635f11ebb6b12df7967854fdb","tid":2210671,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T00:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2a9055b22672eb0ddc2a7da25b63511c0f0bd7","tid":2210671,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"